events.description: The release of wholesale price data for January 2026 in Austria, showing a year-on-year increase of 0.4%.

facts.fact_text: Wholesale prices in Austria increased by 0.4% year-on-year in January 2026.

evidences.evidence_text: Wholesale prices in Austria increased by 0.4% year-on-year in January 2026

facts.fact_text: Wholesale prices for coffee, tea, cocoa and spices rose by 14.7%.

evidences.evidence_text: Significant price increases were seen for coffee, tea, cocoa and spices (+14.7%)

facts.fact_text: Wholesale prices for liquid and gaseous fuels fell by 13.2%.

evidences.evidence_text: wholesale prices fell sharply for other liquid and gaseous fuels and related products (-13.2%)

facts.fact_text: On a monthly basis, wholesale prices rose by 0.7% in January.

evidences.evidence_text: On a monthly basis, wholesale prices rose by 0.7% in January

claims.claim_text: Wholesale price growth is accelerating compared to the previous month.

evidences.evidence_text: accelerating from a 0.1% gain in the previous month

claims.claim_text: Monthly wholesale prices are recovering from a prior decline.

evidences.evidence_text: recovering from a 0.7% decline in the preceding period

evidence.evidence_text: Austria Wholesale Prices Rise Faster in January
wholesale prices fell sharply for other liquid and gaseous fuels and related products (-13.2%)
Other notable contributors included other machinery and equipment (+9.8%)
